title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1992-03-17
lineage: Transfer: Master DAT > Panasonic SV-3800 (spdif out) > Digigram VX Pocket sound card > Panasonic Toughbook (spdif in) > Steinberg Nuendo > WAV 1648
taper: Recording by Dave Brotman & Jeff Metchick
description:
Set I
Box Of Rain
New Minglewood Blues
Loser

Tennessee Jed
Cassidy
Set II
Way To Go Home
Truckin' >
Spoonful >
He's Gone >
Drums >
Space >
I Need A Miracle >
So Many Roads >
Sugar Magnolia

The Weight


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Vince Welnick - Keyboards
Bruce Hornsby - Piano, Accordion
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
